r.com/uploads/2023/08/05animecapture2-6d5a61014181c420512daa7e0ff15c9b-kix.xxe9iqnsvhi1-1024x576.jpg"></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/06animecapture3-6d5a61014181c420512daa7e0ff15c9b-kix.4wvpvu5towhx.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/06animecapture3-6d5a61014181c420512daa7e0ff15c9b-kix.4wvpvu5towhx-1024x576.jpg"></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/07animecapture4-6d5a61014181c420512daa7e0ff15c9b-kix.neil7mgespi.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/07animecapture4-6d5a61014181c420512daa7e0ff15c9b-kix.neil7mgespi-1024x576.jpg"></a></p><p>该动画由人气视频创作者<a href="https://twitter.com/RIRI45309899" target="_blank" rel="noopener">山下RIRI</a>制作，BGM由<a href="https://twitter.com/RyotaSuemasu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sue君</a>负责，讲述了一个女巫（CV：<a href="https://twitter.com/naobou_official" target="_blank" rel="noopener">东山奈绪</a>）使用魔法与和她一起生活的猫们玩游戏的故事。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://twitter.com/z3_cut" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Misumi</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/nana_kaguraaa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nanakagura</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/done_kanda" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dan Tateda</a>将担任负责VTuber设计的插画师， <a href="https://twitter.com/rariemonn765" target="_blank" rel="noopener">rariemonn</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/MegaJujube" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jujube</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/date_list" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Date</a>将担任Live2D建模师。此外，三丽鸥还负责VTuber的原创设计。</p><p>该项目的首批成员正在以试镜的形式招募，截止日期为 9 月 10 日（周日）。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/pastedimage0-6d01228d66b50641c47d778107e23b38-kix.e04mrc9d9omz-300x212.png"></div><div class="card-